\b  
\c 52  
\q1  
\v 1 Nyane, nyane, Ao Sion, 
\q2 hy…õ aho…îden adurade…õ no. 
\q1 Hy…õ wo ntade…õ f…õf…õ no 
\q2 Ao, Yerusalem kurop…în kronkron no. 
